Package pxchat.whiteboard

Class Summary
BackgroundFrame This frame is used to set a new background.
CircleObject This class represents a circle on the paint board.
EllipseObject This class represents an ellipse on the paint board.
FreeHandObject This class represents a path on the paint board.
ImageClearFrame This frame causes the whiteboard to discard all paint objects except the background.
ImageObject This class represents an image on the paint board.
ImageTable This class implements a global image storage were each image has a unique key.
ImageTable.Holder  
LineObject This class represents a line on the paint board.
PaintObject This class is the basis for all objects that can be drawn onto the paint board.
PointObject This class represents a single point on the paint board.
PrimitiveObject This class is the base class for all paint objects that have a color and a line width.
RectObject This class represents a rectangle on the paint board.
